race.description: Christmas Race Day 22 November 2025 Mdn Hcp
race.comment: PRECIOUS GIRL (8) returned for her second campaign with a tenacious on-pace second over 900m at Newcastle. Has further upside to come from the good gate. Goes close. BOBBY (1) Menari gelding from Fluttershy on debut for the Perry yard. Has impressed in all three trials and will prove hard to hold out with Fitzgerald's 1.5kg claim. DIACON (3) Tassort filly from Sutton Forest making her debut for the Bjorn Baker stable. Fitted with four trials and looks well placed on the Gosford circuit from the inside gate. MAJESTIC LEGEND (7) knocked up late when returning for her second prep when fifth over 1000m at Hawkesbury. No shock to see her figure in the placings.
